sub_title: English language trainer at Language Partners
summary: Experienced English Language Instructor with a demonstrated history of working in the professional training & coaching industry. Skilled in English as a Second Language (ESL), Translation, Lesson Planning, Editing, and Instructional Design. Strong education professional with a PGCE (Masters) in Education from Homerton College, University of Cambridge, Master's Degree in Creative and Life Writing from Goldsmiths College, London. Masters in Cognitive Neuropsychology from Vrije Universiteit Amsterdam and CELTA qualification from International House.
